results.deck: Sir Arthur Conan Doyle's legendary detective Sherlock Holmes has met his greatest foe: French gentleman burglar Arsène Lupin. The game follows Maurice LeBlanc's penultimate creation as he continuously challenges England's finest to a duel of wits over the nation's most treasured assets.
